字串(string)資料型態及其運算

string1 = "I love you"

---------replace()取代--------------
string1.replace("love","hate")

---------join()--------------
'_'.join("Dragon")
'x'.join("Dragon")

-------split()---------------
string1.split()

#string2 = 'x'.join("Dragon")
#string2.split(sep='x')

string1.upper()
string1.swapcase()

###有空白==>去除空白#############
string11 = "   I love you  "
string11.strip()

